**Why this license?** This license is inspired by the "fair-code" / Sustainable
Use model (e.g., n8n, GitLab EE). It keeps the source visible and self-hostable
for anyone, while protecting against direct commercial exploitation by hosted
competitors. It is NOT a pure permissive open-source license — it adds a
single use restriction: don't offer this exact service commercially without
permission. This balances openness with the ability to sustain the project.
